### =========================================================
### User Auth API - Membership / Group Admin (RBAC v1)
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN

@tenantId = REPLACE_TENANT_ID
@groupId = REPLACE_GROUP_ID
@membershipId = REPLACE_MEMBERSHIP_ID
@invitationId = REPLACE_INVITATION_ID
@inviteeEmail = staff.user@attestry.io

### 1) Invitation create (SCOPE_TENANT_INVITATION_CREATE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{inviteeEmail}}",
  "groupId": "{{groupId}}",
  "role": "STAFF"
}

### 2) Invitation accept (로그인한 초대 대상자 토큰으로 호출)
POST {{baseUrl}}/invitations/{{invitationId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3) Membership list (SCOPE_TENANT_MEMBERSHIP_VIEW)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4) Membership role update (SCOPE_TENANT_ROLE_ASSIGN + LIVE_RECHECK)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships/{{membershipId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "role": "OPERATOR"
}

### 5) Membership status update (SCOPE_TENANT_MEMBERSHIP_ENFORCE + LIVE_RECHECK)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/memberships/{{membershipId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "SUSPENDED"
}

### 6) Group suspend (SCOPE_TENANT_GROUP_SUSPEND)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/groups/{{groupId}}/suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7) Group unsuspend (SCOPE_TENANT_GROUP_RESUME)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}/admin/groups/{{groupId}}/unsuspend
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
